HCore will create a sort of symlink between the modules descriptors and this folder
Each module descriptor is represented by '.CMP'.

Example:
SL
POINTS TO MODULE
HCore.Modules.HInit.Init
AT PACK
HCore.Modules.HInit

In this example, this file points to the module descriptor of the module "HCore.Modules.HInit.Init" that is inside the module "HCore.Modules.HInit".

SL
POINTS TO FILE
/mods/HCore.Modules.HInit.Init.CMP